summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2015 MERCEDES-BENZ GLK350. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE MANUFACTURER FAILED TO PROVIDE THE PART WITHIN A REASONABLE TIME FRAME FOR MANUFACTURER RECALL NUMBER: 2019010001 (AIR BAGS). THE MANUFACTURER INDICATED THAT THE PART MAY BECOME AVAILABLE IN MID MAY OF 2020. THE DEALER WAS NOT CONTACTED. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT REPAIRED. THE CONTACT HAD NOT EXPERIENCED A FAILURE.
